events.text: Eydoo!? I'm in the middle of something, what is your business here?
Do you think you can get away with stealing my stampede?
I know your plan and I'm all for dealing with... That. But how dare you, Seezee!?
Give it back and we'll think of another plan. I need my elephant!
You don't need it more than I do! This will work just fine.
I see how it is. You leave me no choice...
Stand ready for my power, Seezee!
